HEADWORD: Lighthouse
<hw>Light"house`</hw> <pr>(l⟦imac⟧t"hous`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Lighthouses</plw>
<pr>(l⟦imac⟧t"houz`⟦ecr⟧z)</pr>.</plu> <def>A tower or other building
with a powerful light at top, erected at the entrance of a port, or at
